tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打到頭破血流真係唔係幾好<br />\n請手足弱點打擊 只打手腳 畫面又冇咁血腥 創傷仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35de18ebb75a0c2bfdd8f182f09f3810d2e6b0c","tid":1633960,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"藍絲group 話左邊車門比人開左，導致踩大油撞人"}]}